{ Trap the enemy king to one side of the board. }
1. Qe3 Kc4 { Use the queen to force the king to left side of the board. } { [%csl Gd2][%cal Gd2d8,Gd2a2] } 2. Qd2 Kc5 { keep shrinking the box gradually until you force the king to the last file/rank. } { [%csl Gd3][%cal Gd3a3,Gd3d8] } 3. Qd3 Kc6 { [%csl Gd4][%cal Gd4a4,Gd4d8] } 4. Qd4 Kb5 { take away one more file from the king } { [%csl Gc3][%cal Gc3c8,Gc3a3] } 5. Qc3 Kb6 { Continue shrinking the box. } 6. Qc4 Ka5 7. Qb3 Ka6 { [%csl Gb4][%cal Gb4a4,Gb4b8] } 8. Qb4 Ka7 { [%csl Gb5][%cal Gb5b8,Gb5a5] } 9. Qb5 Ka8 { Alert!
Don't Continue Shrinking the box now. That would lead to stalemate.
Now continue with bringing the king over so that you can deliver checkmate. } 10. Kg2 (10. Qb6) 10... Ka7 11. Kf3 Ka8 12. Ke4 Ka7 13. Kd5 Ka8 14. Kc6 Ka7 { The king is now close enough to deliver checkmate. } 15. Qb7# *


